{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/39371", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/39371/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/39371/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/39371/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/39371", "id": 203830190, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyMDM4MzAxOTA=", "number": 39371, "title": "Non-upper case constant warning misapplied in patterns", "user": {"login": "rpjohnst", "id": 161677, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTY3Nw==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/161677?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst", "html_url": "https://github.com/rpjohnst", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rpjohnst/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 235137, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMzUxMzc=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-lint", "name": "A-lint", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: Lints (warnings about flaws in source code) such as unused_mut."}, {"id": 178802147, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxNzg4MDIxNDc=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/I-needs-decision", "name": "I-needs-decision", "color": "e11d21", "default": false, "description": "Issues in need of decision."}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2017-01-28T20:47:19Z", "updated_at": "2021-05-21T09:42:19Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "A constant with `#[allow(non_upper_case_globals)]` applied still generates a warning when used in a pattern, unless the `match` also has the allow attribute. For example:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\n#[allow(non_upper_case_globals)]\r\nmod keywords {\r\n    pub const If: u32 = 0;\r\n    pub const While: u32 = 1;\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    use keywords::*;\r\n\r\n    // the warning goes away with this attribute:\r\n    // #[allow(non_upper_case_globals)]\r\n    match 0 {\r\n        keywords::If => println!(\"if\"),\r\n        While => println!(\"while\"),\r\n        _ => println!(\"<unknown>\"),\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n[Playground](https://is.gd/jzNZQB)", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/39371/reactions", "total_count": 17, "+1": 17, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/39371/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}